<plot>Dottie's Magic Pockets is the first kids' show that features gay and lesbian families - and it is Super-riffic Fun for everyone! Each 50-minute DVD is filled with catchy songs, cute cartoons - like purplish-pink Princess and her two dads - and Dottie's fabulous puppet friends. Dottie's Magic Pockets takes your child on an educational journey exploring these four areas: social, intellectual, musical, and emotional. It also helps all children understand and appreciate gay and lesbian families. Kids love (and need!) this show!</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?157149</url></doc>
